f the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d54af4f2de06eb3acc663ce2571f0a01285cf59","tid":1390124,"uid":281318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3ba3d290781b6a8f424bad2b0cdf89505262561","tid":1390124,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:49:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=3d6cf40c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=6d4144c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n\t<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</st